In order to upload your website files through FileZilla, please do the following steps.

1)  Open FileZilla FTP client software, and then enter hostname, username and password in the Quick connect Bar.

Now your local site is in the left bar and your remote site is in the right bar.

2) In the remote site, double click on your website directory and then double click on public_html directory.

3) In the local site section, locate your website files and then drag and drop your files from local sites to remote site.

4) You will then get a confirmation that your file has been uploaded successfully.
